1
00:01:25,780 --> 00:01:30,020
[The Vendetta of An]

2
00:01:30,060 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 1]

3
00:01:33,020 --> 00:01:39,180
[Tenth Day of the Seven Month]

4
00:02:00,780 --> 00:02:08,420
[Soon, we will return to Chang'an]

5
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:34,130
In the 28th year of Qiansheng,

6
00:02:34,790 --> 00:02:36,730
the founding emperor fell ill suddenly

7
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,660
and passed away unexpectedly.

8
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:42,070
General of Huben Army, Yan Fengshan, governed the imperial court

9
00:02:42,070 --> 00:02:43,420
and threw the government into chaos.

10
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:46,660
He helped the late emperor's youngest son, Xiao Wenjing, ascend the throne

11
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,950
and killed the feudal lords,

12
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:51,600
causing imperial authority to decline.

13
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:55,210
In the 4th year of Wencheng,

14
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:58,460
the late emperor's eldest son, a feudal lord, Xiao Wuyang,

15
00:02:58,950 --> 00:03:00,680
mobilized troops from the north

16
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:03,190
to overthrow the tyranny.

17
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,120
They travelled 1,300 li southward.

18
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,090
With strict military discipline along the way,

19
00:03:07,170 --> 00:03:08,910
all sides submitted to him.

20
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,660
He arrived in Chang'an,

21
00:03:11,090 --> 00:03:12,460
eliminated the treacherous officials,

22
00:03:13,090 --> 00:03:15,500
and took control of the imperial court.

23
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:39,100
[Taiqing Palace]

24
00:04:03,420 --> 00:04:07,380
[Xiao Wuyang, New Emperor]

25
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:12,060
Unable to bear the defeat, the deposed emperor, Xiao Wenjing,

26
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:16,020
burned himself inside Taiji Hall.

27
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,060
Your Highness,

28
00:04:37,630 --> 00:04:38,410
there were five dead bodies.

29
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:39,940
None of them belonged to the deposed emperor.

30
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:43,780
[Gu Yu, Marquis of Northguard]

31
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:45,850
Have you verified all of them?

32
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:47,470
Apparently, the deposed emperor

33
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,420
slipped and fell

34
00:04:48,420 --> 00:04:49,780
on a hanbaiyu marble staircase when he was young.

35
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:50,570
Because of that,

36
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,130
his upper left molar was chipped.

37
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:54,570
He also fractured his left leg.

38
00:04:55,030 --> 00:04:55,570
All of these

39
00:04:55,710 --> 00:04:56,570
are recorded in the palace records.

40
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:58,450
These dead bodies

41
00:04:58,470 --> 00:04:59,130
might be unrecognizable,

42
00:04:59,910 --> 00:05:00,780
but it is not difficult

43
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:01,890
to verify these injuries.

44
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:05,980
Your Highness,

45
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:08,130
this was just removed from a dead body's stomach.

46
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:26,130
It

47
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,060
still appeared in the end.

48
00:05:29,030 --> 00:05:30,500
It was set up on purpose.

49
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:33,660
They are waging war against Xiao Wuyang.

50
00:05:38,590 --> 00:05:40,340
All subordinates of the city-guarding general,

51
00:05:40,470 --> 00:05:41,450
Li Longjing, have surrendered.

52
00:05:41,910 --> 00:05:43,340
There might still be skirmishes in the city,

53
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:44,820
but it's nothing to worry about.

54
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,010
We've captured all 12 gates of the Capital.

55
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,610
We will set up camps

56
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:49,930
in the south

57
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:50,730
and southwest.

58
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,610
Moreover, the north side of the city

59
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,220
is in our army's control.

60
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,340
The north is secure.

61
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:58,170
What about Yan Fengshan

62
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:00,490
and his army?

63
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,290
Greetings, Your Majesty.

64
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,700
The scene at Taiji Hall

65
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,810
has been examined.

66
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:27,050
The deposed emperor, Xiao Wenjing,

67
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,250
did not die in the fire.

68
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:34,140
This was recovered from the stomach

69
00:06:34,190 --> 00:06:36,020
of one of the dead bodies

70
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:36,810
in Taiji Hall.

71
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,140
I'm sure Your Majesty

72
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:41,140
recognizes the token.

73
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:57,730
Huben Token.

74
00:06:59,390 --> 00:07:00,170
Does it mean

75
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,370
he has abducted

76
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:05,170
that useless brother of mine?

77
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:06,100
Yes.

78
00:07:07,420 --> 00:07:09,340
Xiao Wenjing might be useless,

79
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:10,660
but one can rule the world

80
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:11,980
simply by abducting the emperor.

81
00:07:13,310 --> 00:07:13,900
Perhaps

82
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:16,490
this battle is far from over.

83
00:07:17,510 --> 00:07:18,220
Perhaps

84
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:21,370
it is just the beginning.

85
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,930
Yan Fengshan and the Huben Army have decided to stay hidden

86
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:27,490
because they do not want to face Your Majesty directly.

87
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:30,250
But as long as the deposed emperor is in his hands,

88
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,540
he will surely rise again.

89
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:34,780
A hidden battle

90
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,610
will soon begin.

91
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,930
I am old.

92
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,700
I was careless.

93
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,810
When you are facing Yan Fengshan,

94
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:21,460
no one can win

95
00:08:21,870 --> 00:08:23,410
in one move.

96
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:25,900
I do recommend one particular person

97
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:28,810
if you want to deal with the Huben Army.

98
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:32,760
He understands the army the most in this world.

99
00:08:33,250 --> 00:08:34,850
His father, Liu Ziwen,

100
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,730
is the founder of the Huben Army.

101
00:08:37,180 --> 00:08:38,170
15 years ago,

102
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:40,800
Yan Fengshan led the Huben Army

103
00:08:40,800 --> 00:08:42,100
and betrayed Liu Ziwen.

104
00:08:45,670 --> 00:08:47,560
The Liu clan was annihilated.

105
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:50,440
He

106
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:53,180
got lucky and survived

107
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,460
He is an exceptional talent.

108
00:08:58,390 --> 00:08:59,090
Moreover,

109
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:00,450
he carries a grudge.

110
00:09:01,390 --> 00:09:02,780
After 15 years,

111
00:09:02,950 --> 00:09:04,660
he is now fully prepared.

112
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,730
Many former retainers of the Liu clan

113
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,980
are also helping him secretly.

114
00:09:09,630 --> 00:09:10,850
An exceptional talent?

115
00:09:12,070 --> 00:09:13,140
How does he compare to you?

116
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:14,780
I am old.

117
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:15,930
I'm inferior to him.

118
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,290
In that case, bring him to me.

119
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,220
I will test him myself.

120
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:29,580
Understood.

121
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:33,860
[Huainan]

122
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:46,720
Be careful with that.

123
00:09:47,750 --> 00:09:48,590
There's more over here.

124
00:09:50,170 --> 00:09:51,220
Have some water.

125
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:56,140
In times of crisis,

126
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:57,780
the government is obstructive and the people suffer.

127
00:09:58,270 --> 00:10:00,220
Extraordinary individuals will arise

128
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,810
[Huainan District Office]
like leopards and magpies.

129
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,610
With the momentum of soaring eagles,

130
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:05,220
they achieve remarkable feats.

131
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:07,580
Therefore, extraordinary accomplishments

132
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:10,010
require extraordinary people.

133
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:11,940
How extraordinary.

134
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,610
As extraordinary as I am clueless.

135
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:16,180
You don't need to understand any of that.

136
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:17,490
As long as I

137
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:19,800
[Zhou Mo, Magistrate of Huainan]
and the officials above me understand it.

138
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,130
Just listen to these sentences.

139
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:23,700
Divide and reclaim the land

140
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,530
to restore the dynasty.

141
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:28,060
With Heaven's mandate to suppress the rebels,

142
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,540
no rebellion can't be crushed.

143
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,500
With righteous actions to achieve merit,

144
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:32,890
any achievements can be accomplished.

145
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,300
The sentences are magnificent

146
00:10:35,630 --> 00:10:37,420
and every word is exquisite.

147
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:38,890
All of you

148
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,490
are bumpkins.

149
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:41,980
Don't even dream of writing such an article

150
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,820
even in your next life.

151
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:45,180
Sir,

152
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,420
we specialize in

153
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,700
repairing the roofs and catching chickens

154
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:49,650
for the residents.

155
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:52,340
You cannot compare us to them.

156
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,650
Exactly, sir.

157
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,660
Yes.

158
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,010
That's right, sir.

159
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:56,580
Sir!

160
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:58,130
Sir!

161
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,370
What is it?

162
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,980
The imperial envoy will arrive at the city gates soon.

163
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:04,180
All of you, pull yourselves together.

164
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,820
Come with me to meet the imperial envoy.

165
00:11:07,270 --> 00:11:07,790
Where's Huai'an?

166
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,440
Where's my buddy?

167
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:11,940
Huai'an!

168
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,180
Huai'an!

169
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:21,980
Huai'an!

170
00:11:22,790 --> 00:11:23,610
The imperial gazette is here!

171
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:28,660
[Xie Huai'an]

172
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,370
Be careful.

173
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:35,460
I just got it.

174
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,420
That's all you harvested after half a day?

175
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:44,460
The weather is good today.

176
00:11:44,870 --> 00:11:46,530
I'm letting the paddy dry in the sun.

177
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,940
Sure. If you say so.

178
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:50,820
I've read

179
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:51,730
the imperial gazette.

180
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:52,580
The latest issue

181
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,530
is from a month ago.

182
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,980
It's fine even if it's late.

183
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:57,420
At least, we know

184
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:58,820
what is happening out there.

185
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:00,890
Huainan is

186
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,610
remote and desolate.

187
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,730
What happens outside

188
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,100
has nothing to do with this place.

189
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:25,220
The weather is changing.

190
00:12:27,510 --> 00:12:27,890
Yes.

191
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:30,100
Rain is coming from behind the mountain.

192
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:32,890
Ziya.

193
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:34,850
Look at this article.

194
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:39,060
It has been a month

195
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,220
since Xiao Wuyang

196
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,700
attacked Xigu Mountain City.

197
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,460
After passing Xigu Mountain City,

198
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,010
it's only 300 li

199
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:47,850
from Chang'an.

200
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:49,890
There's no choke point

201
00:12:52,270 --> 00:12:53,250
in-between to defend against any attack.

202
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,060
I'm sure Chang'an

203
00:12:56,670 --> 00:12:58,100
won't be captured so easily.

204
00:12:58,390 --> 00:12:59,610
The Imperial Guards are in charge

205
00:12:59,630 --> 00:13:00,370
of Chang'an's defense.

206
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:01,850
The soldiers

207
00:13:02,550 --> 00:13:04,180
are all from noble families.

208
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,850
They have adequate military strength,

209
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:08,060
but look at General Li.

210
00:13:08,630 --> 00:13:09,940
His name is Li Longjing.

211
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,300
He is a coward.

212
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,100
Chang'an

213
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,650
might have been captured already.

214
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,060
That's impossible.

215
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:20,100
An imperial envoy has come from Chang'an.

216
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,610
Zhou Mo is probably waiting

217
00:13:21,630 --> 00:13:22,610
at the gates to welcome him

218
00:13:22,790 --> 00:13:23,700
with your proclamation condemning the rebels.

219
00:13:24,790 --> 00:13:25,300
What?

220
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:34,720
[Huainan]

221
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:35,220
Sir.

222
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,420
They are so slow, sir.

223
00:13:36,870 --> 00:13:37,650
Are you waiting for your wife?

224
00:13:37,790 --> 00:13:38,530
How fast do you expect them to be?

225
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,580
You are useless.

226
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:46,780
[Huainan District Office]

227
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,650
What is it? Is the imperial envoy here?

228
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,180
I wrote a congratulatory article

229
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,300
for the new emperor's ascension.

230
00:13:56,390 --> 00:13:57,060
Help me find it, quickly.

231
00:13:57,270 --> 00:13:58,370
[Zhang Haoran]
There's no congratulatory article here.

232
00:13:58,390 --> 00:14:00,410
Didn't you write to condemn the rebels?

233
00:14:00,670 --> 00:14:02,400
Zhou Mo took it to meet the imperial envoy.

234
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:03,180
That article must not be submitted.

235
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:04,980
One and a half months ago,

236
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:05,980
Xiao Wuyang led the army

237
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,010
and captured Xigu Mountain City.

238
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:08,020
The city

239
00:14:08,150 --> 00:14:09,060
is only 300 li away from Chang'an.

240
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:11,850
There's no choke point in between to defend against any attack.

241
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,530
I'm sure Chang'an won't be captured

242
00:14:13,550 --> 00:14:14,220
that easily.

243
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:15,220
It has already been captured.

244
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:16,820
The imperial envoy

245
00:14:16,820 --> 00:14:17,730
serves the new emperor.

246
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,780
If Zhou Mo submits the article,

247
00:14:19,870 --> 00:14:21,170
we'll all be dead.

248
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:22,380
- That's... - Enough.

249
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:23,260
Look for it, quickly.

250
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:25,970
When did you write it?

251
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:27,060
Two years ago.

252
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:28,380
Two years ago?

253
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:29,420
Can you predict the future or something?

254
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:32,730
Found it.

255
00:14:33,270 --> 00:14:34,210
They are here.

256
00:14:34,390 --> 00:14:35,210
Play the music!

257
00:14:35,210 --> 00:14:36,330
Quick, sound the drum.

258
00:14:43,150 --> 00:14:44,380
Why does he look like a eunuch?

259
00:14:44,790 --> 00:14:45,420
Look like a eunuch?

260
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:46,500
He is a eunuch.

261
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,970
It's my first time seeing one.

262
00:14:48,970 --> 00:14:50,180
Stop talking from now on.

263
00:14:58,550 --> 00:15:01,020
I, the Magistrate of Huainan District, Zhou Mo,

264
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:03,380
[Huainan]
greet the imperial envoy.

265
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:06,610
You may stand, Magistrate.

266
00:15:06,790 --> 00:15:08,500
Thank you, Imperial Envoy.

267
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:19,330
Huainan District is so remote.

268
00:15:19,910 --> 00:15:21,090
I think

269
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,610
I've travelled 70 li of mountainous roads

270
00:15:22,610 --> 00:15:24,570
to arrive here from the county.

271
00:15:24,630 --> 00:15:25,810
Sir,

272
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:27,970
Huainan might be remote,

273
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:31,300
but every land here belongs to the emperor.

274
00:15:31,510 --> 00:15:32,730
The people of Huainan

275
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:35,180
are also blessed by His Majesty's grace.

276
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:37,300
You have a silver tongue.

277
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:38,060
Imperial Envoy,

278
00:15:38,270 --> 00:15:39,840
I've prepared

279
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:40,720
the best inn

280
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:41,970
in the district town

281
00:15:42,270 --> 00:15:43,660
to give you

282
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:45,020
a warm welcome.

283
00:15:46,270 --> 00:15:46,730
That's right.

284
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:47,810
One more thing.

285
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:48,550
We have

286
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:50,450
prepared an article

287
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:51,730
