When you were 17 years old,

406
00:21:11,110 --> 00:21:11,780
you carried

407
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,650
a tattered pack

408
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:15,030
and came to Huainan,

409
00:21:15,030 --> 00:21:15,890
a remote place,

410
00:21:16,270 --> 00:21:18,090
like a homeless man.

