00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:26,220
All of us knew

416
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:28,810
you were destined for great things.

417
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:31,500
We treated you well

418
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:33,540
not because we wanted you to help us out

419
00:21:33,830 --> 00:21:35,740
when you achieved success one day,

420
00:21:36,310 --> 00:21:37,570
but we did it out of sincerity.

421
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:41,130
However,

422
00:21:41,790 --> 00:21:43,020
you are also aloof.

423
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:45,740
Yes.

424
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:47,810
But that's who I am.

425
00:21:54,870 --> 00:21:56,220
Careful.

426
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:58,780
Lie here and count the stars

427
00:21:59,200 --> 00:21:59,810
as your punishment.

428
00:22:06,750 --> 00:22:07,940
Stars!

429
00:22:08,790 --> 00:22:09,540
Stars,

430
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:11,610
