Yan Fengshan.

451
00:23:28,110 --> 00:23:29,130
Yan Fengshan?

452
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:31,700
His influence spreads across the imperial court.

453
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:34,570
But times have changed.

454
00:23:35,510 --> 00:23:36,410
Xiao Wuyang

455
