00:24:05,350 --> 00:24:06,220
Are you trying

463
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:08,460
to clear your family's name?

464
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:19,810
Everyone is dead.

465
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:23,300
There's no use clearing their name.

466
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:29,020
I'm going to take revenge.

467
00:24:42,070 --> 00:24:42,500
All right.

468
00:24:42,880 --> 00:24:44,060
Go back and rest.

