499
00:27:13,820 --> 00:27:15,160
he just needs to start a fire, boil some water,

500
00:27:15,190 --> 00:27:16,010
and cook them.

501
00:27:16,820 --> 00:27:17,600
You are right.

502
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:19,250
