522
00:30:06,310 --> 00:30:07,330
I am a member of the Huben Army.

523
00:30:11,380 --> 00:30:12,530
Huai'an, I didn't lie to you.

524
00:30:14,140 --> 00:30:15,530
I also didn't lie to Haoran and the rest.

525
00:30:15,990 --> 00:30:17,850
What I have been showing all of you

526
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:20,120
