536
00:30:45,620 --> 00:30:46,330
Huai'an.

537
00:30:47,340 --> 00:30:49,010
I might be one of the Huben Army,

538
00:30:49,470 --> 00:30:50,680
but I've never

539
00:30:50,860 --> 00:30:52,770
killed anyone until today.

540
00:30:53,550 --> 00:30:55,570
I didn't expect the first person I would kill

541
00:30:55,790 --> 00:30:57,330
