566
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:07,610
When I was ten years old,

567
00:33:08,550 --> 00:33:10,120
my father died as well.

568
00:33:14,750 --> 00:33:18,090
The whole Huben Army defected and killed him.

569
00:33:19,340 --> 00:33:20,530
I can't die.

570
00:33:23,140 --> 00:33:25,250
I must get revenge on the Huben Army.

571
00:33:26,510 --> 00:33:28,400
I'll kill any Huben soldiers I see

572
00:33:30,030 --> 00:33:32,090
until none of them are left.

573
00:33:41,950 --> 00:33:43,720
