00:33:47,030 --> 00:33:48,050
I did it.

577
00:33:49,550 --> 00:33:50,120
Huai'an.

578
00:33:50,660 --> 00:33:51,530
We are here to send you off.

579
00:34:03,620 --> 00:34:04,330
What happened?

580
00:34:14,190 --> 00:34:14,880
Zhou Mo.

581
00:34:15,860 --> 00:34:16,570
Sir!

582
00:34:16,580 --> 00:34:17,290
- Sir! - What happened?

583
00:34:19,750 --> 00:34:20,530
Don't ask.

584
00:34:21,710 --> 00:34:23,090
It's not his fault.

585
00:34:24,750 --> 00:34:26,680
Don't tell anyone.

586
00:34:28,580 --> 00:34:29,250
Don't...

587
00:34:30,420 --> 00:34:32,120
Don't trouble him.

588
00:34:33,550 --> 00:34:34,200
We all

589
00:34:36,230 --> 00:34:37,610
have our own reasons.

590
00:34:39,420 --> 00:34:39,960
Zhou Mo.

591
00:34:40,620 --> 00:34:41,370
- Zhou Mo. - Sir!

592
00:34:42,230 --> 00:34:43,010
Zhou Mo!

593
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:46,160
- Sir! - Sir!

594
00:34:46,990 --> 00:34:47,720
Sir!

595
00:34:57,030 --> 00:34:57,960
What have you done?

596
00:34:58,270 --> 00:34:59,880
That's Zhou Mo!

597
00:35:02,820 --> 00:35:03,850
Stay away from me

598
00:35:06,100 --> 00:35:07,720
if you don't want to die.

599
00:36:10,780 --> 00:36:12,610
[Autumnal Equinox: thunder begins to soften,]

600
00:36:12,610 --> 00:36:14,740
[insects find space to make nests, and water begins to solidify.]

601
00:36:33,380 --> 00:36:34,600
The water is chill

602
00:36:35,540 --> 00:36:36,690
and the weather is cold.

603
00:36:37,750 --> 00:36:39,690
Travelers, move along.

604
00:36:40,310 --> 00:36:43,080
Those near the riverbank, stay away from the shore.

605
00:36:51,900 --> 00:36:53,480
Color me surprised.

606
00:36:58,590 --> 00:37:00,210
This place could kill you.

607
00:37:00,900 --> 00:37:01,960
Why did you come back?

608
00:37:03,590 --> 00:37:04,920
Only one person is buried here.

609
00:37:05,750 --> 00:37:07,040
It's not a dangerous place.

610
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:09,880
The real danger is Chang'an,

611
00:37:10,860 --> 00:37:11,850
70 li away from us.

612
00:37:12,940 --> 00:37:14,730
It seems like you are passing by indeed.

613
00:37:16,230 --> 00:37:17,210
Then, I won't be

614
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:19,880
sharing this fish with you.

615
00:37:23,380 --> 00:37:24,480
I'm going back to Chang'an.

616
00:37:26,460 --> 00:37:27,690
I don't know if I'll leave alive.

617
00:37:29,980 --> 00:37:31,170
So, I come to see you

618
00:37:33,150 --> 00:37:33,960
before I enter Chang'an.

619
00:37:44,590 --> 00:37:45,290
Right.

620
00:37:47,230 --> 00:37:48,170
You

621
00:37:48,860 --> 00:37:50,040
are bound to return one day.

622
00:37:54,670 --> 00:37:55,170
Yes.

623
00:37:56,710 --> 00:37:57,560
Your younger sister

624
00:37:58,190 --> 00:37:59,210
went to Chang'an as well.

625
00:38:00,190 --> 00:38:01,520
She went to study.

626
00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:03,040
Perhaps

627
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:04,250
she is an imperial scholar now.

628
00:38:08,750 --> 00:38:09,400
I know.

629
00:38:10,670 --> 00:38:11,880
Both of you are so far apart.

630
00:38:12,820 --> 00:38:13,600
How did you know?

631
00:38:15,230 --> 00:38:16,480
She has been writing letters to me.

632
00:38:18,020 --> 00:38:19,000
I've also been replying to her letters.

633
00:38:19,340 --> 00:38:20,520
Why wouldn't you reunite with her?

634
00:38:27,460 --> 00:38:28,170
I dare not.

635
00:38:30,380 --> 00:38:32,000
It's best not to reunite with her forever.

636
00:38:33,940 --> 00:38:34,880
None of my family

637
00:38:36,940 --> 00:38:38,440
ended up well.

638
00:38:44,790 --> 00:38:45,850
The people of the Liu clan

639
00:38:47,340 --> 00:38:48,650
suffer a harsh fate.

640
00:38:51,900 --> 00:38:53,520
Her name has been changed.

641
00:38:56,310 --> 00:38:57,520
Hopefully, she can live her life in peace.

642
00:38:58,380 --> 00:38:59,960
You've changed your name as well.

643
00:39:02,310 --> 00:39:03,440
You must be safe.

644
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:06,040
Come.

645
00:39:53,500 --> 00:39:55,820
[Chang'an]

646
00:40:03,830 --> 00:40:04,630
Mr. Huai'an,

647
00:40:04,940 --> 00:40:06,780
both of us are here to pick you up.

648
00:40:09,590 --> 00:40:11,130
It's the beginning of winter today and it's snowing.

649
00:40:11,470 --> 00:40:12,280
Thank you, both of you.

650
00:40:13,300 --> 00:40:13,800
Mister,

651
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:14,460
let me carry it.

652
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:15,010
Open the gates.

653
00:40:18,030 --> 00:40:18,530
This way.

654
00:41:03,060 --> 00:41:05,660
♪Memories are arrows flying against the wind♪

655
00:41:06,220 --> 00:41:09,100
♪Piercing through what should be forever♪

656
00:41:09,340 --> 00:41:13,980
♪They wake me to find our story ended♪

657
00:41:15,820 --> 00:41:18,780
♪When has time ever been kind♪

658
00:41:19,460 --> 00:41:21,940
♪Or shown mercy to anyone?♪

659
00:41:22,340 --> 00:41:23,820
♪I ride across the mountains and return♪

660
00:41:23,820 --> 00:41:26,980
♪Still cloaked head to toe in night♪

661
00:41:28,500 --> 00:41:31,460
♪The bitter sea knows no shore, the wind no sleep♪

662
00:41:31,620 --> 00:41:34,500
♪You remain far back in the past♪

663
00:41:34,860 --> 00:41:35,820
♪I drift in a lone boat♪

664
00:41:35,820 --> 00:41:37,940
♪Searching the depths of the abyss♪

665
00:41:38,260 --> 00:41:41,060
♪Before old dreams scatter and fade♪

666
00:41:41,380 --> 00:41:44,380
♪Why is life so short♪

667
00:41:44,500 --> 00:41:47,300
♪And filled with partings?♪

668
00:41:47,660 --> 00:41:50,820
♪Only now do I see fate knows only the lash♪

669
00:41:51,020 --> 00:41:53,900
♪And grants no mercy♪

670
00:41:54,380 --> 00:41:55,940
♪Alas♪

671
00:41:55,940 --> 00:41:59,940
♪Time vanishes in an instant into dust and smoke♪

672
00:42:00,820 --> 00:42:02,820
♪Ashes of regret♪

673
00:42:02,820 --> 00:42:06,420
♪Burn through my remaining years♪

674
00:42:07,180 --> 00:42:08,820
♪Alas♪

675
00:42:08,820 --> 00:42:12,740
♪This body is trapped in destiny's cold prison♪

